{
  "1714850": {
    "name": "Twilight Wars: Declassified",
    "steam_appid": 1714850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/24be2b4aae191d4d27a3ac117d909295.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Twilight Wars: Declassified 2.0&quot; is an updated <strong>free demo version</strong> of the main game. It includes two missions that will introduce you to the world of &quot;<strong>Twilight Wars</strong>&quot; and demonstrate the basic mechanics of the game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/9c076b3ca7d261a72a440c82c289f581.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mid-21st century. The largest multinational corporations have acquired the status of states and have thrown off the shackles of law and morality. In the absence of any deterrent measures, industrial espionage, theft of developments, and the assassination of competitors have reached alarming proportions, evolving into a full-scale war for information, technology, and resources that, over time, has begun to affect the lives of ordinary citizens.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main adversary of the new rulers of the world is the Anonymous Arbitration Agency, an independent espionage organization created to protect people from corporate tyranny and regulate covert wars. However, Triple-A’s operations have unfortunately interfered with too many interests. During a swift attack, unknown assailants destroyed all bases and neutralized the vast majority of operatives. The only survivors were Shi, the artificial intelligence that runs the organization, and you. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/968750fe0e6cedb53219e7ea7a03e506.poster.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=345 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/968750fe0e6cedb53219e7ea7a03e506.webm?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now you make the fate of the Agency and the world! Together with Shi, you must revive the Triple-A, avenge your fallen comrades, and strike back at the powerful corporations. Rebuild and upgrade the base, recruit and train personnel, complete missions, and expand your sphere of influence. This world will not tolerate weakness - show your strength!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/591e847d69fa47b1a3f18eb6bcc1a2ea.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=191 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Action-packed Dungeon-crawler with turn-based combat in a cyberpunk espionage setting, featuring an original approach to the “permadeath” mode. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building an effective and cohesive team of charismatic agents with conflicting alignments and complex characters.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/5ba8e4da9b9e7c1755b46cc9e16102b6.poster.avif?t=1746627790\" width=612 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/5ba8e4da9b9e7c1755b46cc9e16102b6.webm?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/5ba8e4da9b9e7c1755b46cc9e16102b6.mp4?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >For each mission, the choice of skills and specialisations of agents requires an individual approach: rescuing hostages, going in two squads, fighting bosses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/4a9c68e170a1bf6f3983f53bc71e4382.poster.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/4a9c68e170a1bf6f3983f53bc71e4382.webm?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/4a9c68e170a1bf6f3983f53bc71e4382.mp4?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Building your own cosy base with high-tech modules for healing, rest, training and reviving agents. And with a kitty cat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/7919f67d856c15c434d4b3cb19883af4.poster.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/7919f67d856c15c434d4b3cb19883af4.webm?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/7919f67d856c15c434d4b3cb19883af4.mp4?t=1746627790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dealing with moral dilemmas as the story progresses and building rapport with the head of the agency, an artificial intelligence named Shi, will determine one of the game's many endings. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original graphic and musical style in a unique atmosphere of &quot;cozy cyberpunk&quot;.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714850/extras/7bd93ac79868a407188dc1443a71cf11.avif?t=1746627790\" width=614 height=243 /></span> </p>",
